text: @gaeliclass149 So feel your despair, Terter, way down under here in Melbourne, Australia. Please know that your heroic efforts are acknowledged here, & though we can't support you in person, many many peeps support you in spirit. We must do our best here to prevail over COVID-19 in your honour https://t.co/mltJphF16h
